lexicon = 
  heat, poke, red, sit, yam, gawk, lag, tim, doop, back

Normal state
  Back - return to normal state
  Tim - change focus
  Yam - windows
    Tim - minimize
    Doop - unminimize
    Gawk - snap right
    Sit - snap left
  Poke - launch
    heat - firefox
    gawk - terminal
  Doop - type a key
    Yam - press f
    Red - press 0
    Tim - press 1
    Sit - press 2
    Lag - press enter
  Red - Close current thing
  Gawk - no-op
  Heat - no-op
  Sit - no-op
  Lag - no-op


Default State:
  yam: change to windows state
  poke: change to launching state
  tim: change focus
  red: close window (not implemented)
  doop: change to browsing state
  back: change to default store
Windows State:
  poke: change to launching state
  sit: snap left
  tim: minimize window
  gok: snap right
  doop: unminimize window
  back: change to default store
Launching State:
  poke: change to launching state
  heat: launch Firefox
  gok: launch terminal
  back: change to default store
Brwosing State:
  yam: press f
  poke: change to launching state
  sit: press 2
  tim: press 1
  lag: press enter
  red: press 0
  back: change to default store